quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  62,9,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, jab pukara jaye namaz ke liye jumaa ke din to Allah ke zikr ki taraf daudo aur khareed-o-farokht chodh do. Yeh tumhare liye zyada bethar hai agar tum jaano"
  62,10,"Phir jab namaz poori ho jaye to zameen mein phayl jao aur Allah ka fazl talash karo aur Allah ko kasrat se yaad karte raho, shayad ke tumhein falaah (kamiyabi/prosperity) naseeb ho jaye"
  62,11,"Aur jab unhon ne tijarat (business) aur khel tamasha hote dekha to uski taraf lapak gaye aur tumhein khada chodh diya. Insey kaho, jo kuch Allah ke paas hai wo khel tamashey aur tijarat se behtar hai aur Allah sabse behtar rizq (sustenance) dene wala hai"